Package mdxmlconverter.element

Class DataTypeConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • mdxmlconverter.element.DataTypeConverter
  • public class DataTypeConverter
extends java.lang.Object
    Class providing static methods to convert strings representing data types or replaces the id of a PackagedElement with its name, if the datatype is a reference

    dschoenicke

      • convertDataType

        public static java.lang.String convertDataType​(java.lang.String elementReference,
                                               DataType dataType)
        Static method converting the string representing the data type of a given Extension or sets the data type to the id of a PackagedElement if the data type is a reference
        Parameters:
        elementReference - the id of a PackagedElement if the data type is a reference, is Null otherwise
        dataType - the Actual holding the data type string to be converted if the data type is primitive, is Null otherwise
        Returns:
        the converted data type name or the element reference

      • convertDataType

        public static java.lang.String convertDataType​(java.lang.String elementReference,
                                               Actual actual)
        Static method converting the string representing the data type of a given Actual or sets the data type to the id of a PackagedElement if the data type is a reference
        Parameters:
        elementReference - the id of a PackagedElement if the data type is a reference, is Null otherwise
        actual - the Actual holding the data type string to be converted if the data type is primitive, is Null otherwise
        Returns:
        the converted data type name or the element reference

      • generateDataTypeString

        public static java.lang.String generateDataTypeString​(Extension extension)
        Static method converting the qualified Magic Draw XML name of a primitive type to its simple name
        Parameters:
        extension - the Extension containing the ReferenceExtension which contains the qualified name
        Returns:
        the simple name of the data type

      • convertElementID

        public static java.lang.String convertElementID​(java.lang.String elementID,
                                                TemporaryModel tmpModel)
        Static method converting references to PackagedElements to the name of the corresponding UmlElement
        Parameters:
        elementID - the id of the PackagedElement
        tmpModel - the TemporaryModel containing a mapping of element ids and UmlElements
        Returns:
        the converted element name if the elementID was a reference or the input string if it is an already converted primitive type
